-- Freeworld Coatings of South Africa Gets Approach From Japan's Kansai Paint
-- B y   N i c k y   S m i t h
-- 2010-11-05T10:31:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-05/freeworld-coatings-of-south-africa-has-had-approach-from-kansai-paint.html
Freeworld Coatings Ltd. has had an
unsolicited bid from Japan’s Kansai Paint Co., a statement from
South Africa’s competition authorities shows.  Kansai has accumulated a stake larger than 26 percent of
Freeworld and Freeworld is concerned about the antitrust
implications of a takeover, the statement shows.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nicky Smith in Johannesburg at 
 nsmith38@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
